text: Lena Niang (born 20 September 1996) is a Senegalese basketball player for Temple Owls and the Senegalese national team.Afrobasket.com profile She represented Senegal at the 2019 Women's Afrobasket.2019 Women's Afrobasket profile ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Centers (basketball) Category:People from Bowie, Maryland Category:Senegalese women's basketball players
